channel.title: Well, I have a quick question for those of you old schoolers
channel.description:
Okay, so, just a quick question for all'a ya... For RSPS's that are a revision 194, what date/time period is that from if you're looking at JaGeX's Runescape? Like, is it 2006 or before it? 'Cause a lot of people have 317's that they say are "2006 remakes" (Which there are just sooo damn many people attempting that. Come on, guys, actually finish your work lol) but 194 is a bit before that. Is it 2005-2006, or still the year of 2006?
ALSO! Sorry if this isn't the correct section for this sort of a question, I wasn't able to find a more appropriate category.
